    ".His Wolf Entertainment has had a profit participation deal with Universal Television since 2004, allowing him to retain nearly half of his shows? profits when they sell into syndication.",
    "Wolf is one of the pioneers of the \"linear binge,\" putting shows from a shared universe back-to-back on a single night of television",
    "The company now oversees seven network shows and a streaming show on Amazon, producing nearly 150 episodes of television per year and overseeing more than 3,000 writers, actors and producers."
  ],
